node.text:
I now understand why mums always say they are happy when the family enjoys the food they have prepared no matter how tiring. 😊 As long as they are happy, I will be happy too.

Ingredients for 🦞 Porridge:
Lobsters
Prawns
Korean lalas
Dried scallops
Rice
Oil
Salt
Sugar
Julienned ginger
Spring onions
@fj.mama surprisingly cos never made this before and so I am very pleased with it! 😊
@serafina_in_faith didn’t know you are half korean! ❤️ Yes, I also remember the porridge that Zahn had in Seoul when he was few months old and that was super yummy!
My Korean grandma used to make abalone or lobster brown rice porridge for us. Such nostalgia when I see your post😋😋
@melvasg it’s pretty 👍🏻! When the main ingredient is good, you really don’t need much work or effort to make it good.
@happyzboys I see all the super fresh stuff u got delivered!! Makes me hungry!  Yea the good stuff works its own magic!
@turquoise__sky the family loves it so I guess it is. 😊
@la_f_am reminds me of the yummy porridge I had in Seoul! I wanna go back!! 😊
@cloverchar4babies got the lobster, prawns and lalas from @mr.fishmongersg
Where did you get such fresh lobsters 🦞 😍
@menemjeffff haha 😆 and I am hungry now too!
Omg this looks incredible!!!😍 My mouth is watering at the sight🤤🤤🤤
@jessiedlim try it, dear! Let me know how it goes. 😊
Look so yummy! I’m going to try cooking! 😋😋😋
@mizprissy yeah it’s really 👍🏻! Very fresh  and sweet!!
@asilentcarousel we decided to cook this at the very last minute! Thanks to my husb who suggested this after I told him I managed to get some🦞. 😊
@jessluvzs thanks to the fresh seafood! It won’t be nice without them! 😊
